column13: Exemplary- Demonstrates profound ability to complete the task and shows they have mastered it.
column15: Proficient - Demonstrates ability to preform the task in acceptable way
column17: Apprentice - Shows they have the ability to preform the task but have not reached an acceptable performance level
column19: Beginner - Has little ability to preform the task, still room for much knowledge and improvement
